Are you not of more value
than they?

00:05:04.387 --> 00:05:06.514
And which of you
by being anxious

00:05:06.597 --> 00:05:11.811
can add a single hour
to his span of life?

00:05:11.894 --> 00:05:13.730
Therefore do not
be anxious, saying,

00:05:13.813 --> 00:05:14.897
"What shall we eat?"

00:05:14.981 --> 00:05:17.108
"What shall we drink?"

00:05:17.191 --> 00:05:20.278
or
"What shall we wear?"

00:05:20.361 --> 00:05:24.323
For the Gentiles
seek all these things,

00:05:24.407 --> 00:05:29.996
and your heavenly Father
knows you need them all.

00:05:30.079 --> 00:05:33.499
But seek first
the kingdom of God

00:05:33.583 --> 00:05:36.252
and His righteousness,

00:05:36.335 --> 00:05:40.506
and all these things
will be added to you.

00:05:40.590 --> 00:05:45.136
So whatever you wish
that others would do to you,

00:05:45.219 --> 00:05:48.556
do also to them,

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:52.351
for this is the Law
and the Prophets.

00:05:52.435 --> 00:05:55.271
[in background] Judge not,
